<h1 class=" head mt-3">{{blogname}}</h1>
<div class="banner-text mainblog-img mt-5 mb-4">
  <h5 class="ban-txt">{{subject}}</h5>
  <h4 class="ban-txt m-2">{{type}}</h4>
  <h6 class="ban-txt2">{{course}}-{{semester}}-Calicut University</h6>
  <br />
  <p class="ban-txt">studocu.herokuapp.com</p>
</div>

<article class="content">
  <p class="article">
    Download <b>{{subject}}</b> {{type}} of Calicut University {{course}} {{semester}} Students.
    From below link you can download the {{semester}} {{type}} of {{course}} course {{subject}} pdf for University of
    Calicut School of Distance Education.name of university is calicut university.
  </p>
  <br />
  <div class="container mt-3">

    <div class="row">
      <h5 class="g">University -</h5>
      <h5 class="t">Calicut University</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <h5 class="g">Course -</h5>
      <h5 class="t">{{course}}</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <h5 class="g">Semester -</h5>
      <h5 class="t">{{semester}}</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <h5 class="g">Subject -</h5>
      <h5 class="t">{{subject}}</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <h5 class="g">Type -</h5>
      <h5 class="t">{{type}}</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <h5 class="g">Name -</h5>
      <h5 class="t">{{file.filename}}</h5>
    </div>

  </div>

  <a class="mt-4 btn btn-lg btn-block btn-primary" href="{{file.link}}">Click here to Download</a>

  <div class="mt-5">
    <iframe src="{{file.link}}"></iframe>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-3">
    <h4><b>Tag</b></h4>
    <a class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block mt-3" href="/{{course}}/{{semester}}/{{subject}}/{{type}}">More
        {{course}}-{{subject}}-{{semester}}-{{type}}</a>
  </div>
  <br />
</article>

<div class="main">
  <h4 class="mt-2"><b>What is Studocu..?</b></h4>
  <p class="article mt-4 mb-4">studocu is a place for college students. here you can download every documents you want
    for studies..</p>
  <h4 class="mt-2"><b>What you can find here..?</b></h4>
  <ul class="mt-4 ml-3">
    <li>Previous question papers</li>
    <li>Modal question</li>
    <li>Study materials</li>
    <li>Syllabus</li>
    <li>PDF books</li>
    <li>Time tables</li>
    <li>Project</li>
    <li>Results</li>
  </ul>
  <h4 class="mt-4"><b>Whats our mission...?</b></h4>
  <h6 class="text mt-4">Studocu is a place for college students. here you can download every documents you want for
    studies. most of the notes and and question papers are already on the internet. but everything is scattered
    throughout websites and its all hard to find. so we are trying to make them all group. then everyone can easly
    found it. you can also support us by adding the link of documents in the correct place.. Now we have only calicut
    university.. in future we
    add others too.. you can take an <a class="g" href="/myprofile"><b>Account</b></a> on this app and save your
    documents in Saved
    List. Just click on your Browsers bar and add this to your homescreen. This site is made for mobiles</h6>
    <br/>
    <br/>
</div>


